dict.string:
Stencils to use for modelling a software system, based on Simon Brown's C4 model. These stencils support the Context, Container, and Component diagrams and look and feel like Simon's models from his book "Software Architecture for Developers". You can buy the book on Leanpub to support Simon: https://leanpub.com/software-architecture-for-developers/ More information on the C4 model can be found here: https://leanpub.com/software-architecture-for-developers/read#c4 If you have any feedback on these stencils, please contact me on Twitter: @dennislaumen
Created by: Dennis Laumen
